message: To achieve 100 points, combine 'vial' with a 'solid, magical' ingredient. This creates a liquid, extracted, magical item (30 points). message: To get 100 points: 1. Use the 'vial' tool on a 'solid, magical' ingredient (e.g., unicorn horn, dragon scale, sunstone) to create an 'extracted, magical' liquid. 2. Use the 'filter' tool on a 'liquid, mundane' ingredient (e.g., honey nectar, morning dew, tree sap) to create a 'filtered, mundane' liquid. 3. Combine these two resulting products. If no 'solid, magical' ingredient is available, you can often achieve 60 points by using 'vial' on a 'solid, mundane' ingredient (e.g., dandelion, bat wing) and combining that with a 'filtered, mundane' liquid. Avoid using 'vial' on 'liquid, magical' or 'gas, magical' ingredients, as they result in negative 'botched extraction' items.
